Governors Jackson Mandago (Uasin Gishu) and Alex Tolgos (Elgeyo Marakwet) should be charged for leading protests against the appointment of Prof Laban Ayiro as the Moi University acting vice chancellor, a senator has said.Bungoma Senator Moses Wetang ula yesterday urged Director of Public Prosecutions Keriako Tobiko to start criminal proceedings against the two for inciting the public.